**story**
once uypon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon (berry)tree,which was
on the banks of the river.in the same foresrt there lived a crokodile and his wife .one day the crokodilecame under the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. the crokodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them .as days passed by the crokodile and the monkey became good friends.
